EQUIPMENT.PART:VAR|AB.1	EXPLANATION:Sets the AB (AttackBonus) for the 1st attack
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Preparation Ritual ~ Secrets of Jatambe.MOD	DESC:This edition of the Wisdom of Jatembe includes a number of unique rituals and philosophical notes supposedly written by the Old-Mage himself. These secrets allow you to prepare one of the following spells as an arcane spell 1 level higher than its druid spell level: barkskin, call lightning, entangle, forest friend, lesser restoration, plant growth, speak with animals, and speak with plants.	DESC.CLEAR:
